sub_title: Assistant Professor of Computational Linguistics, Vrije Universiteit Amsterdam (VU Amsterdam)
summary: I am Assistant Professor of Computational Linguistics and Natural Language Processing (NLP) at Vrije Universiteit Amsterdam (VU Amsterdam). My research focuses on developing communicative robots and adaptive dialogue systems using formal linguistic and computational methods.
